data.description: Welcome to Vail Vista Estates! Quiet serenity and peaceful nature await you at this wonderful 4bd/2bath +den home on an acre lot. Magnificent views of the surrounding mountain ranges abound from all sides of the property making for a truly lovely home site. Modern upgrades are also seen throughout this standout home. The kitchen shows beautifully with hand stained white oak cabinetry, ''Desert Infinity'' Quartzite  is breathtaking! New appliances and hammered copper sink looking out to more mountain views pull it all together! Another great feature is having 5 separate spaces. 4 private bedrooms and a bonus room for den or study and no wasted space makes it easy to fall in love. The primary suite offers real hardwood floors and custom fitted walk in closet. A/C unit by Daikin has Inverter Tech which is ultra quiet and ultra efficient coupled with a smart thermostat that is smarter and cooler than the rest! High Ceilings are another breath of fresh air. The list goes on, Absolutely wonderful covered patio space with views make it simple for parties, BBQ's or just relaxing. Next is the 3 car garage with electrical upgrades with dedicated circuits, 220 outlet and LED shop lights akin to a workshop space! All this in a great Vail location with schools and shopping nearby. Come see your new home now!
